These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, dannemann
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is not to the right of the dannemann-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Cigar   | dannemann | alhambra |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, pony
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is not to the left of the owner of the pony##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Pet   | pony | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: british, japanese
1. the british is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
2. the japanese is on the left or right of the british##3
3. the british is not to the right of the british##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Nationality   | british | japanese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
